	
	Convert your HTML to entities, copy the returned code and paste it 
	between <pre></pre>. Add the style to your CSS to highlight the syntax.
	
	Created by Camilo Kawerin <http://kawerin.com.ar> from Con Vista Al Mar 
	<http://convistaalmar.com.ar/>.
	
